channel.title: Can't Login
channel.description: Okay, for some reason, when people sometimes logout they can't log back in. It will say Ipbanned try again in 5 minutes(Not really Iped). I have to refresh the server. And another thing, when someone is walking it lags. This never happened before, I don't know what I changed for it to happen(Walking/running). Can someone help me fix these problems please? 317 Delta base. I don't care what you say about delta, it's a great base. So, thanks in advanced. Hopefully this problem gets fixed. If you need anything, client class, player class, etc., just reply. :P
